{"word":"H5883 - עֵין רֹגֵל - ʻÊyn Rôgêl - ane ro-gale' - En-rogel","slug":"H5883","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עֵין רֹגֵל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻÊyn Rôgêl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ane ro-gale'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>En-rogel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>עין רגל</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>‛êyn rôgêl</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>ane ro-gale'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> En-rogel = \"fount of the fuller\" <ol><li>a place near Jerusalem on the border between Judah and Benjamin and from which the permanent source of the pool of Siloam comes</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H5869\">H5869</a> and the act. part. of <a href=\"#/H7270\">H7270</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4599\">H4599</a>, <a href=\"#/H5770\">H5770</a>, <a href=\"#/H5869\">H5869</a>, <a href=\"#/H5871\">H5871</a>, <a href=\"#/H5872\">H5872</a>, <a href=\"#/H5873\">H5873</a>, <a href=\"#/H5874\">H5874</a>, <a href=\"#/H5875\">H5875</a>, <a href=\"#/H5876\">H5876</a>, <a href=\"#/H5877\">H5877</a>, <a href=\"#/H5879\">H5879</a>, <a href=\"#/H5880\">H5880</a>, <a href=\"#/H5881\">H5881</a>, <a href=\"#/H5882\">H5882</a>, <a href=\"#/H5884\">H5884</a>, <a href=\"#/H5885\">H5885</a>, <a href=\"#/H5886\">H5886</a>, <a href=\"#/H6044\">H6044</a>, <a href=\"#/H6046\">H6046</a>"}]}